In other more recent
ones, it's everyone's

00:46:18.840 --> 00:46:21.680
infected, when you
die, you're a zombie.

00:46:21.680 --> 00:46:23.520
They're really
different outcomes.

00:46:23.520 --> 00:46:26.420
I don't know if you had any
