He was trying to use the
zombies as a metaphor.

00:46:45.680 --> 00:46:47.840
So in the first one, he
kept it vague, right?

00:46:47.840 --> 00:46:52.904
There was the satellite from
outer space that had come back,

00:46:52.904 --> 00:46:54.320
and it was somehow
linked to that.

00:46:54.320 --> 00:46:56.087
But it could've been
space radiation.

00:46:56.087 --> 00:46:57.670
And he was saying
he explicitly didn't

00:46:57.670 --> 00:47:00.090
care about what caused it.

00:47:00.090 --> 00:47:02.430
He just wanted them to be there.

00:47:02.430 --> 00:47:06.894
In fact, he put the nail
in our coffin of our theory

00:47:06.894 --> 00:47:07.810
about zombie movement.

00:47:07.810 --> 00:47:08.310
Them.

00:47:08.310 --> 00:47:10.980
But I'll tell you
about that later.

00:47:10.980 --> 00:47:13.350
So I think what happened
was because the early zombie

00:47:13.350 --> 00:47:15.350
cultures didn't really
care about the mechanism,

00:47:15.350 --> 00:47:17.760
there were just lots of
different explanations.

00:47:17.760 --> 00:47:19.440
From a biological
standpoint it doesn't

00:47:19.440 --> 00:47:21.060
seem like that
would be the case.

00:47:21.060 --> 00:47:24.290
There is one-- so
